name: First Sunday Concert Series (#4)
shortDescription: Artists for February are three doctoral candidates: pianists Sichum Gao and Jing Li, and violinist Ziqian Ye.
fullDescription: Featuring: Three internationally acclaimed performers from the School of Music, University of Arizona, and a fully restored A.B. Chase 1893 nine-foot concert grand piano with tonal qualities rivaling the best 2025 models.
title: First Sunday Concert Series (#4)
